<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fire Breathing Workshop — Edinburgh</title>
<meta name="description" content="Learn to breathe fire safely in a hands-on, one-day workshop in Edinburgh. Beginner-friendly, small groups, full safety training included.">

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=Work+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --ink-black: #16110D;
    --ink-black-2: #241A14;
    --ink-black-3: #2E211A;
    --flame-amber: #FFB347;
    --flame-orange: #FF6A1A;
    --flame-red: #E8380D;
    --cream: #FFF3E0;
    --cream-dim: #D8C6AE;
    --line: rgba(255,243,224,0.12);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--ink-black);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  h1, h2, h3, .display {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .mono {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  a { color: inherit; }

  .wrap {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(22,17,13,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  nav .wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--flame-orange); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--flame-orange);
    color: var(--ink-black) !important;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .nav-links a:not(.nav-cta) { display: none; }
  }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    width: 900px; height: 900px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,56,13,0.25) 0%, rgba(255,106,26,0.08) 40%, transparent 70%);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: pulse 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.08); }
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--flame-amber);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 28px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--flame-amber);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 7.5rem);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .flame-word {
    background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--flame-amber) 0%, var(--flame-orange) 35%, var(--flame-red) 60%, var(--flame-orange) 85%, var(--flame-amber) 100%);
    background-size: 300% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    animation: flicker 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes flicker {
    0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .flame-word, .hero-glow { animation: none; }
  }

  .hero-sub {
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-meta-item .mono {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .hero-meta-item strong {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 44px;
    background: var(--flame-orange);
    color: var(--ink-black);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 18px 38px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(255,106,26,0);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,106,26,0.35);
  }

  /* ---------- SECTION SHARED ---------- */
  section { padding: 110px 0; }
  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--flame-orange);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-lede {
    max-width: 620px;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* ---------- WHAT YOU LEARN ---------- */
  .learn-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .learn-card {
    background: var(--ink-black-2);
    padding: 32px 28px;
  }
  .learn-card .mono {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--flame-amber);
  }
  .learn-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    text-transform: none;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 12px 0 10px;
  }
  .learn-card p {
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ---------- INCLUDED / PRICING ---------- */
  .price-block {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--ink-black-2), var(--ink-black-3));
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 56px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .price-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 36px 24px; }
  }
  .included-list { list-style: none; }
  .included-list li {
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }
  .included-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .included-list .tick {
    color: var(--flame-orange);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .price-card {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--ink-black);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 40px 28px;
  }
  .price-card .mono { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--cream-dim); }
  .price-amount {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--flame-orange);
    margin: 8px 0;
  }
  .price-amount span { font-size: 1.5rem; vertical-align: super; }
  .price-card .btn-primary { margin-top: 24px; width: 100%; }

  /* ---------- SAFETY ---------- */
  .safety-box {
    border: 1px solid var(--flame-orange);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,106,26,0.06);
  }
  .safety-box .mono { color: var(--flame-orange); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }
  .safety-box p { color: var(--cream-dim); }
  .safety-box p + p { margin-top: 14px; }

  /* ---------- INSTRUCTOR ---------- */
  .instructor {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .instructor { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .instructor-photo {
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    background: var(--ink-black-2);
    border: 1px dashed var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 24px 0;
  }
  .faq-item h3 {
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    text-transform: none;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .faq-item p { color: var(--cream-dim); }

  /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 48px 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--flame-orange); text-decoration: none; }

  ::selection { background: var(--flame-orange); color: var(--ink-black); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="nav-logo">🔥 Jinn Fire <span style="color:var(--flame-orange)">& Flow</span></div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#learn">What You'll Learn</a>
      <a href="#safety">Safety</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="#pricing" class="nav-cta">Book Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow mono">Edinburgh · Beginner Friendly · Small Groups</div>
    <h1>Learn to<br><span class="flame-word">Breathe Fire</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A hands-on, one-day workshop teaching you to breathe fire safely and confidently — taught in person, in small groups, with full safety training built in from the start.</p>

    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="mono">Date</span>
        <strong>[Insert workshop date]</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="mono">Location</span>
        <strong>[Insert venue, Edinburgh]</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="mono">Duration</span>
        <strong>[e.g. 3 hours]</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="#pricing" class="btn-primary">Reserve Your Spot →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="learn">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag mono">The Skills</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">What You'll Learn</h2>
    <p class="section-lede">Everything is broken down step by step — no experience needed. By the end of the day you'll understand the physics of fire breathing, how to handle fuel and torches safely, and be ready to practise on your own.</p>

    <div class="learn-grid">
      <div class="learn-card">
        <span class="mono">01</span>
        <h3>Fuel &amp; Equipment</h3>
        <p>What fuel to use, what to avoid, and how to properly maintain your torches.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="learn-card">
        <span class="mono">02</span>
        <h3>Safety Protocol</h3>
        <p>Fire safety fundamentals, spotting, extinguishing, and what to do if something goes wrong.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="learn-card">
        <span class="mono">03</span>
        <h3>Breath &amp; Technique</h3>
        <p>The core technique itself — breath control, positioning, and building the muscle memory to do it safely.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="learn-card">
        <span class="mono">04</span>
        <h3>Practise &amp; Feedback</h3>
        <p>Supervised practice time with hands-on correction, so you leave with real reps under your belt.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="safety">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag mono">Before You Book</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Safety First</h2>
    <div class="safety-box">
      <span class="mono">Please read</span>
      <p>[Insert your standard safety disclaimer here — age restrictions, health conditions that may prevent participation (e.g. asthma/respiratory conditions), participant responsibility, and any waiver you require attendees to sign.]</p>
      <p>[Insert insurance/liability statement if relevant.]</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="instructor">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag mono">Your Instructor</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Taught By Julian</h2>
    <div class="instructor">
      <div class="instructor-photo">[Your photo here]</div>
      <div>
        <p class="section-lede" style="margin-bottom:0;">[Insert a short bio — your experience performing, how long you've been fire breathing, any notable shows/events, and why you started teaching workshops.]</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="pricing">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag mono">Book Your Spot</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Pricing</h2>
    <div class="price-block">
      <ul class="included-list">
        <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Full one-day hands-on tuition</li>
        <li><span class="tick">✓</span> All fuel and torches provided</li>
        <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Full safety briefing and supervised practice</li>
        <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Small group size — [insert max number]</li>
        <li><span class="tick">✓</span> [Insert anything else included, e.g. certificate, photos, refreshments]</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="price-card">
        <span class="mono">Per Person</span>
        <div class="price-amount"><span>£</span>100</div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Book on Eventbrite →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="faq">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag mono">Questions</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">FAQ</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Do I need any experience?</h3>
      <p>No — this workshop is designed for complete beginners.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is it safe?</h3>
      <p>[Insert your answer — safety measures in place, supervision ratio, etc.]</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What should I wear?</h3>
      <p>[Insert clothing guidance — natural fibres only, tie back hair, etc.]</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What's your cancellation policy?</h3>
      <p>[Insert refund/reschedule policy.]</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p>© <span id="year"></span> [Your Business Name]. Fire breathing workshops in Edinburgh.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;">Questions? <a href="mailto:[your@email.com]">[your@email.com]</a></p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

</body>
</html>
